Android 8.1 based
Latest kernel & mesa with support for bleeding edge intel/amd hardware.
Latest firefox for android desktop.
Fully re-worked modern UI/UX.
Performance optimization of core apps.
Windows win+p like manual controll of displays. Multi screen/monitor with different resolution, app window can go across screens.
Audio mixer with multi audio stream & multi device support.
Firmware TCMM standard support.
Bio authentication support: fingerprint, iris.
FIDO password-less usage.
Ocloud（Openthos cloud）based file exchange between users, Wifi-direct/Bluetooth for local devices.
Better cloud integration and dedicated client.
Multi-instance for single app.
GUI installer via openthos live system.
Integrated android studio for developers edition with linux subsystem.
Better appstore, sync with google play store's x86 branch.
